Media Queries : 

Purpose of media queries:
    used to display the elements based on screen size.

/* min-width is to say, if screen has minimum width then apply this transistion.  */
@media only screen and ( min-width:400px){
    body{
        background-color: #e00808;
    }
}


/* min-width is to say, if screen has maximum width then apply this transistion.  */
@media only screen and ( max-width:400px){
    body{
        background-color: #2230aa;
    }
}

/* Applying both to the screen.  */

@media only screen and (min-width:700px) and (max-width:1200px){
    body{
        background-color: green;
    }
}